THE PEOPLE WHO ARE DESIROUS OF SUPERIOR PLEASURE!
Even though the sexual pleasure
…..is distressingly inferior,
The people who indulge in it
…..forego the other pleasures!
The people who are desirous
…..of immersing in the ocean
of superior pleasure of House of Heaven,
…..Will they fall
into the sludge of worldly pleasure?
…..No! They wouldn't!

